original_title: Jose Rizal: Sa Landas ng Paglaya
overview: A 35-minute documentary about Jose Rizal’s life and heroic deeds, Jose Rizal: Sa Landas ng Paglaya shows the national hero’s works including El Filibusterismo, which tackles how the revolution would fail if it’s just for “personal interest”.
title: Jose Rizal: Sa Landas ng Paglaya
